Inclusion Criteria:

* puerpera;
* hypertensive;
* use of methyldopa during pregnancy at a minimum dose of 750 mg / day, for at least 07 days before delivery

Exclusion Criteria:

* Use of other antihypertensive medications or illicit drugs that may interfere with maternal hemodynamics, and / or Con

